txt.en: '[placeholder], I suppose you have accomplished more by yourself in just a short time than all the Men of Stangard could do in a month.\n\n'I cannot thank you enough. Let us talk further, for I believe Stanric has a desire to meet with you.'

'You inspired Stanric beyond anything I could have done, my friend! I think things will be different around here now.\n\n'Sithric will no longer share in the leadership of Stangard, and we will be able to fend for ourselves without interference again.'

'You have certainly caught Stanric's attention with all the good you have done...but unfortunately you have caught Sithric's as well.\n\n'I believe Stanric wants to thank you personally, away from the eyes and ears of Th√©oden King's envoy.'
Gadda wishes to thank you for your hard work on behalf of Stangard.
